{"tid":2235971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"PK鄧狂改口「擘大眼講大話」","createTime":"2020-10-09T06:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T10:53:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":274,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"b195aa2b02b6b5da6ed03766507d40d67a24010f","tid":2235971,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:08:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/V4R4T7PTXVAKRKUIXLVIW5FWRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FV4R4T7PTXVAKRKUIXLVIW5FWRQ%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=9d089a90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FV4R4T7PTXVAKRKUIXLVIW5FWRQ%2F&h=651ea7a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/V4R4T7PTXVAKRKUIXLVIW5FWRQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nPK鄧狂改口「擘大眼講大話」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SnslDrwpnwtDZJ58v3AWUdFzzrs=/5832x3944/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TO6VNP5G7NGBFAGHRUSZAQRK4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSnslDrwpnwtDZJ58v3AWUdFzzrs%3D%2F5832x3944%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTO6VNP5G7NGBFAGHRUSZAQRK4A.jpg&h=8f552bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧炳強<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12港人8月23日被中國海警拘捕，一直被秘密拘禁，直至自由亞洲電台引爆消息，警務處長鄧炳強始回應稱「睇媒體公佈先知」，又稱28日才收到內地當局通報。特首林鄭月娥死攬警隊，稱警方「冇任何角色」。但本報連日。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：機管局警方打壓記招滅聲<br />\n<br />\n本報得悉8月23日早上9時25分至9時52分，在飛行服務隊直升機上的警員已從警方陸上指揮中心得悉，12人快艇落入中國海警手中，警方亦確認「任務完成」，絕非至8月28日才知悉事件。<br />\n<br />\n12港人被捕消息傳出後，傳媒只能查問警方是否知悉，鄧炳強8月27日見記者時輕鬆應對，稱「呢件事我睇媒體公佈先知」，又稱直至那一刻「未收到內地相關單位通報事件」，表示這次「不是兩地跨境合作行動」。雖然親共陣營多番恐嚇，部份家屬不願噤聲，公開回應事件並質疑警方配合中國海警將12港人送中。警方發聲明反擊，稱家屬指控失實，強調「8月28日才接獲中國執法部門通報事件」。鄧炳強9月29日出席油尖旺區議會質詢時顯得早有預備，強調12人是「通緝犯並涉及嚴重罪行」，又指「警方最後接獲的消息已是12人被刑事拘留」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭死攬 反斥本報抹黑<br />\n<br />\n本報10月5日揭發飛行服務隊派機「護送」快艇出海，政府事前並非不知情。林鄭翌日仍死撐警方「冇任何角色」，不點名批評本報「抹黑香港政府」、攻擊警方和揑造事實，對香港社會不健康。保安局長李家超亦緊跟口徑，斥本報「混淆視聽、轉移視線」，希望市民「擦亮眼睛」。"},{"pid":"88474f4af8a2e95ba28de07d8ce6fb6b6e6e1818","tid":2235971,"uid":41423,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:10:54.000Z","msg":"中港雙勾不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9251fb4b82705cf8ff693d177b9d8ea56708ef79","tid":2235971,"uid":121197,"like":163,"dislike":1,"score":162,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:14:03.000Z","msg":"你唔公開啲資料釋除公眾懷疑<br />\n然後傳媒走去求證搵到料就話人抹黑<br />\n邊個信你呀？"},{"pid":"7ddccf4fe43398eb2e752b8c8c749ef362031de9","tid":2235971,"uid":256059,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:14:29.000Z","msg":"其實直接認左佢咪仲好 ....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a1b217171476c0f96c155c9fee5cd2dbebb510","tid":2235971,"uid":269202,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:15:22.000Z","msg":"妓女除左廢up人地係抹黑都無招"},{"pid":"4dbdf72764ac48e0d6c95f713dd5513ac166dd39","tid":2235971,"uid":306614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:16:28.000Z","msg":"the style of sanction 11"},{"pid":"04ccf7ddcd0ec195daad1de8a3a7eed3c36b76c3","tid":2235971,"uid":254383,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"7ddccf4fe43398eb2e752b8c8c749ef362031de9","tid":2235971,"uid":256059,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:14:29.000Z","msg":"其實直接認左佢咪仲好 ....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:17:44.000Z","msg":"港共有呢個覺悟，就唔會玩到被制裁"},{"pid":"f70048595729312ac4a13e7729baadd9b6c8cc56","tid":2235971,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9251fb4b82705cf8ff693d177b9d8ea56708ef79","tid":2235971,"uid":121197,"like":163,"dislike":1,"score":162,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:14:03.000Z","msg":"你唔公開啲資料釋除公